rows.label: tev999903_SEL0031
rows.name: This BLADE operative is standing by for orders.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999903_MSG2001
rows.name:
Understood. You'll now be able to receive support
from my division.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999903_MSG2101
rows.name:
Please leave the division-support duties to me.
We will give you everything we've got![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999903_MSG3001
rows.name: I'll show you what I'm capable of.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999903_MSG3101
rows.name: I assure you, I will not let you down.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999903_MSG5001
rows.name: I'm sorry, but I don't have time to talk right now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999903_MSG5101
rows.name:
I'm so sorry to have wasted your time like this,
but I'm busy with something else right now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev999903_MSG5102
rows.name: Could we possibly continue this later?[ST:wait ]
